Package pl.polsl.adam.fudala.tvprog.controller

package pl.polsl.adam.fudala.tvprog.controller
Controller package with main and reading from file

Controller package contains the main method where reading from file and various other methods are called. It also contains the class used for reading from file and GUI class for editing data.

2.0
